{"tid":255362,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓南部被IS佔領 杜特爾特宣布棉蘭老島戒嚴","createTime":"2017-05-24T00:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T10:16:44.000Z","uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4e5ab0eddf9aaf0a69c27d4f51ced38ed7d234","tid":255362,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:06:06.000Z","msg":"菲律賓軍方與伊斯蘭武裝份子在南部爆發衝突，總統杜特爾特宣布棉蘭老島戒嚴六十日，並縮短俄羅斯訪問行程，提早回國應對局勢。效忠伊斯蘭國的激進組織馬巫德集團，以及恐怖組織阿布沙耶夫，昨日下午在棉蘭老島的馬拉維市與軍方爆發激戰。武裝份子佔據醫院及監獄，升起伊斯蘭國的旗幟，又燒毀多間房屋。最少一名軍人死亡，八人受傷。今次是菲律賓在一九七二年以來，首次有總統宣布戒嚴。國防部說，軍人在掃盪恐怖組織據點時，引發槍戰，目前已控制局勢。"},{"pid":"821a42e4e6e0486f8d1a35d5b60561aa651d2cef","tid":255362,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:07:53.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a4bdefe72751b838454c895a2aaf7d6f0063f5","tid":255362,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:07:59.000Z","msg":"香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cec4b163244387bc1eadf21635651d9d9fea9c7","tid":255362,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:08:30.000Z","msg":"僕人國家？"},{"pid":"402e6d6423362df6add953fd49ac9b0e4653f75d","tid":255362,"uid":22737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:08:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0f1745475be0d22dee49d5a9bc30abbb812b82c","tid":255362,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:13:24.000Z","msg":"咁少人死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知今次邊個會幫口/拖呢"},{"pid":"4668a0c9de8d6c91cec591ade0edef301dbacf95","tid":255362,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T00:16:05.000Z","msg":"班軍隊夠唔夠is打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c563a15e7a7baf4c84d4cb43ed6d05aa3a8472b7","tid":255362,"uid":17980,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci